StockPulse UI build completed successfully.

Files modified:
- /app/nextjs-project/app/globals.css - Updated with Luxury Minimal theme (gold accent, sharp corners, warm neutrals)
- /app/nextjs-project/app/page.tsx - Complete StockPulse portfolio intelligence app

Features implemented:
1. Dashboard screen with full report rendering and summary tiles
2. Report History screen with localStorage persistence
3. Settings screen with ticker management, email delivery, and schedule configuration
4. Sample data toggle for demo mode
5. Agent status panel showing all 5 agents
6. Schedule management (pause/resume/sync email) via @/lib/scheduler
7. Collapsible report sections (Executive Summary, Price Movements, Sentiment, Technicals, Recommendations, Risk, Market Overview)
8. Generate Report Now button with rotating loading messages
9. Email delivery integration via Report Delivery Agent
10. ErrorBoundary wrapping all content
